<HL>
   EC Unemployment Declines
</HL>
<DATE>
05/15/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   EUROP
</CO>
<LP>
   BRUSSELS -- Seasonally adjusted unemployment of the 12
